#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/overview.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The darkroom view is where you develop your images. The center panel contains the image currently being edited.\n"
msgstr ""
"La Camera Oscura è dove sviluppi le tue immagini. Il pannello centrale "
"contiene l'immagine attualmente in elaborazione.\n"

#. type: Title #
#: content/darkroom/overview.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "zoom"
msgstr "ingrandimento"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/overview.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Middle-click on the center panel cycle between \"fit to screen\", 1:1 and 2:1 zoom. \n"
msgstr ""
"Click di centro sul pannello centrale intervalla lo zoom tra \"adatta allo "
"schermo\", 1:1 e 2:1. \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/overview.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Alternatively you can zoom between 1:1 and \"fit to screen\" by scrolling with your mouse. Scroll while holding the Ctrl key to extend the zoom range to between 2:1 and 1:10.\n"
msgstr ""
"Alternativamente puoi fare zoom tra 1:1 e \"adatta allo schermo\" "
"utilizzando la rotella del mouse. Tieni premuto Ctrl mentre usi la rotella "
"per estendere la portata dello zoom tra 2:1 e 1:10.\n"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/darkroom/darkroom-view-layout.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "darkroom view layout"
msgstr "disposizione della Camera Oscura"

#. type: Title #
#: content/darkroom/darkroom-view-layout.md
#: content/lighttable/lighttable-view-layout.md content/map/map-view-layout.md
#: content/print/print-view-layout.md
#: content/tethering/tethering-view-layout.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "left panel"
msgstr "Pannello di sinistra"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/darkroom/darkroom-view-layout.md
#: content/lighttable/lighttable-view-layout.md
